description._content: "Bogart Bros. ------ GENERAL GROCERY, PROVISION, --AND--- Crockery Store Is stocked with full lines of all season- able Goods-- ORANGES, LEMONS, CANDIES, APPLES, CANNED GOODS, PICKLES, BISCUITS, RAISINS, CURRANTS, FIGS, PEELS, NUTS, SAUCES, TEAS CROCKERY Dinner Sets, Tea Sets, Toilet Sets, Lamps, Vases, Fancy Dishes, Glassware, Odd Pieces, all to be sold at prices to suit the times. GIVE US A CALL --AGENT FOR-- FLEISCHMAN'S Compressed Yeast --AND-- SALADA CEYLON TEA ---------- BOGART BROS., St. George Street, Deseronto." Advertisement from Deseronto Tribune, 29 November 1895, for the Bogart Brothers' grocery store in St. George Street, Deseronto, Ontario.
